ility, faith, forgiveness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Makhul reported: When Allah blessed David with Solomon, peace be upon him, he said, \u201cO my son, what is the most beautiful?\u201d Solomon said, \u201cThe tranquility of Allah and faith.\u201d David said, \u201cWhat is the ugliest?\u201d Solomon said, \u201cUnbelief after faith.\u201d David said, \u201cWhat is the sweetest?\u201d Solomon said, \u201cThe\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18460,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/07\/salat-bayt-al-maqdis-al-quds\/","url_meta":{"origin":24893,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jerusalem: Pray in Masjid al-Aqsa, or send gifts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 7, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Maymunah reported: She said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, tell us about the Sacred House in Jerusalem.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt is the land of the gathering and the Resurrection. Go there and pray, for one prayer in it is like a thousand\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3042,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/24\/pilgrims-makkah-madinah-quds\/","url_meta":{"origin":24893,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Pilgrimage: No religious travel but to Mecca, Medina, Jerusalem","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not undertake a religious journey but to three mosques: the Sacred Mosque in Mecca, the Mosque of the Messenger of Allah, and the Furthest Mosque in Jerusalem.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1189, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1397 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5959,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/07\/hikmah-sulayman-ibn-dawud\/","url_meta":{"origin":24893,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sulayman: Wisdom of Solomon, son of David","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\u201cThere were two women each of whom had a child. A wolf came and took one of their children, so one woman said, 'It has taken your child!' The other woman said, 'No, rather it has taken your child!'\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33028,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/seek-refuge-entering-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":24893,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seek refuge from Satan when entering mosque","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered the mosque, he would say, \u201cI seek refuge in Allah Almighty, in his noble countenance, and in his everlasting authority from the accursed Satan.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 466 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/24893","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=24893"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/24893\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=24893"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=24893"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=24893"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}